<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Audi R8 V10 Plus Guide</title>
  <style>
    /* General Styles */
     body {
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #000000, #1a1a1a); /* Black gradient */
      color: #e0e0e0; /* Light text for contrast */
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); /* Semi-transparent white background */
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3); /* White glow */
      border-radius: 10px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px); /* Frosted glass effect */
    }

    h1, h2 {
      color: #ffffff; /* White for headings */
    }

    h1 {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-top: 30px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      padding-bottom: 10px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #ffffff; /* White border */
      display: inline-block;
    }

    p, ul {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: #e0e0e0;
    }

    ul {
      list-style-type: none;
      padding-left: 0;
    }

    li {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      padding-left: 20px;
      position: relative;
    }

    li::before {
      content: "â€¢";
      color: #ffffff; /* White bullet points */
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
    }

    /* Card Styles */
    .card {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); /* Semi-transparent white background */
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3); /* White glow */
      padding: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }

    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5); /* White glow on hover */
    }

    /* Images Section */
    .images {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }

    .images img {
      width: 60%; /* Make the image responsive */
      height: auto; /* Maintain aspect ratio */
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3); /* White glow */
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .images img:hover {
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    /* Video Section */
    .video-container {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding: 20px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); /* Semi-transparent white background */
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3); /* White glow */
    }

    .video-container iframe {
      max-width: 100%;
      height: 400px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      border: 5px solid #ffffff; /* White border */
    }

    /* Responsive Design */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .images img {
        max-width: 100%;
      }

      .video-container iframe {
        height: 250px;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
      }

      h2 {
        font-size: 1.8rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Audi R8 V10 Plus Guide</h1>

    <!-- Overview Section -->
    <div class="card">
      <h2>Overview</h2>
      <p>The Audi R8 V10 Plus is the pinnacle of Audi's sports car lineup, combining breathtaking performance with everyday usability. Powered by a naturally aspirated V10 engine, the R8 V10 Plus delivers an exhilarating driving experience, with razor-sharp handling and a luxurious interior. It's a true supercar that embodies Audi's commitment to innovation and engineering excellence.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Key Features Section -->
    <div class="card">
      <h2>Key Features</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Engine:</strong> 5.2-liter naturally aspirated V10 producing 602 horsepower and 413 lb-ft of torque.</li>
        <li><strong>Top Speed:</strong> Over 205 mph (330 km/h).</li>
        <li><strong>Acceleration:</strong> 0-60 mph in just 3.2 seconds.</li>
        <li><strong>Weight:</strong> 3,494 lbs (1,585 kg) thanks to its lightweight aluminum and carbon fiber construction.</li>
        <li><strong>Exclusivity:</strong> A limited-production model, making it a rare and desirable supercar.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Performance Section -->
    <div class="card">
      <h2>Performance</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Power Output:</strong> 602 horsepower and 413 lb-ft of torque.</li>
        <li><strong>Transmission:</strong> 7-speed S tronic dual-clutch automatic gearbox.</li>
        <li><strong>Braking:</strong> Carbon-ceramic brakes for exceptional stopping power.</li>
        <li><strong>Handling:</strong> Quattro all-wheel drive and magnetic ride suspension for maximum grip and stability.</li>
        <li><strong>Track Capability:</strong> Designed to deliver exceptional performance on both the road and the track.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Technology Section -->
    <div class="card">
      <h2>Technology</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Aerodynamics:</strong> Advanced aerodynamics with a rear spoiler and diffuser for optimal downforce.</li>
        <li><strong>Lightweight Construction:</strong> Aluminum space frame and carbon fiber components for reduced weight.</li>
        <li><strong>Interior:</strong> Luxurious and driver-focused cockpit with premium materials and advanced technology.</li>
        <li><strong>Exhaust System:</strong> Sport exhaust system for a thrilling and powerful sound.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Single Image Section -->
    <div class="images">
      <img src="https://uploads.audi-mediacenter.com/system/production/media/20165/images/cfc5a0a024c0044ed217db7fa0dc8453a56275ca/A153933_web_2880.jpg?1698206858" alt="Audi R8 V10 Plus Image">
    </div>

    <!-- Video Section -->
    <div class="video-container">
      <h2>Learn More About the Audi R8 V10 Plus</h2>
      <iframe
        width="560"
        height="400"
        src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/IYnHl8T9QII" <!-- Replace with a relevant Audi R8 V10 Plus video -->
        title="YouTube video player"
        frameborder="0"
        allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
        allowfullscreen
      ></iframe>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>